tafsir[49]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,"Allah woondirii Fello ngo O yewtidi e Annabi Muusaa ngon."
  52,2,"O woondiri kadi Deftere winndannde nden."
  52,3,"E …óeri fontorii…ói wa Defte jippinaa…óe …óen."
  52,4,"O woondiri kadi Suudu ndu Malaa'ika'en wuurniri ndin rewugol Allah ka kammu."
  52,5,"O woondiri kadi kammu toowungu, wonu ngu kippoodi e leydi ndin."
  52,6,"O woondiri kadi maayo hebbiniraango ndiyam ngon."
  52,7,"Pellet, lepte Joomi maa …óen an Nulaa…óo, ko yanooje e heefer…ìe …ìen, feere mun alaa."
  52,8,"Alaa ko du√±ana…ìe …óe, haa …óe ronka yanude e ma…ì…ìe."
  52,9,"√ëalnde kammu ngun dillirta dillere, ngu folwo hollirde daragol Darngal ngal."
  52,10,"Pelle …óen woni e sottugol nokku majje, watta yahugol."
  52,11,"Haray nden √±alnde, halkaare e hayrere woodanii fennu…ìe lepte …óe Allah kammbirani yeddu…ìe …ìen."
  52,12,"∆Åen wonu…ìe e jumpugol fija e nder meere, hara …ìe tefaa fii ummital e caakagol."
  52,13,"√ëalnde …ìe du√±iroytee doole ka Yiite Jahannama du√±annde."
  52,14,"∆Åe wi'anoyee nde √±alnde : awa ko ngee Yiite woni ko fennayno…óon, fewndo Nulaa…ìe mon …ìen hul…ìiniraynoo on nge."
  52,15,"E ko mbilewu woni …óee lepte …óe suti…óon? Kaa hara on alaa e yi'ude?"
  52,16,"Mee…óee nguleeki ngee Yiite sumon nge ! Mu√±√±i…óon …óum maa hara on mu√±√±aaki, fow no fota e mon. On yo…ìetaake hannde, si wanaa ko geddi e keeferaaku ko gollayno…óon kon aduna."
  52,17,"Pellet, hulir…ìe Joomi mun …ìen …óoftagol yamiraa…ói Makko wo…ó…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, hino e Aljannaaji e naamaaji maw…ói, …ói ta∆¥ondirtaa."
  52,18,"Ko …ìe dakmitoray…ìe dakammeeji √±aametee e njaram e desal ko Allah okki …ìe, Joomi ma…ì…ìe da…ónda …ìe lepte Jahiimi …óen. ∆Åe maliree da√±ugol dakamme yela ma…ì…ìe on, e da…óndeede lepte."
  52,19,"∆Åe wi'anee ontuma : √±aamee yaron kala ko yi…óu…óon, ko hanndu…ìe e mun, wata on hulu lorra ko √±aamoton maa ko yaroton kon. ∆äum ko njo…ìdi mon, e golle mon laa…ìu…óe …óen aduna."
  52,20,"Hara ko on so…ì…ìindii…ìe e hoore dan…óe cu…óinaa…óe weertindiraa. Men resini …ìe kadi rew…ìe yoo…óa gitee…ìe."
  52,21,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe, genyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol kadi jokki …ìe e gom…óinal ngal, Men tawtindinay …ìe e geyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol, fii no …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …ìuu…ìira e fee ma…ì…ìe, hay si …ìen golliraano wano ma…ì…ìe. E hoore Men …óuytanoytaa…ìe huunde e baraaji golle ma…ì…ìe …óin; tawde ne…ó…óo kala ko tiginnde e bon…ói …ói o faggitii …óin, gooto ronnditantaako mo ko golli kon."
  52,22,"Men …ìeydanii …ìee yim…ìe Aljanna, nooneeje e muuyantee…ói e kala ko …ìe tuuyetee e teewu."
  52,23,"Hi…ìe jaaondira ka nder Aljanna ton : √±eddu…óe …óe jillaa njaram wa'u…óam wa njaramji goo aduna; woni ko siwrinta adda cona-cana maa ko sabimbinta bakkaatu."
  52,24,"Hara sukaa…ìe no eltanaa…ìe hino wanngoo e ma…ì…ìe, wa'u…ìe wa ka≈ã≈ãe reenaa…óe, hakkee ko …ìe jalbi."
  52,25,"Wo…ó…ìe e yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen fewtita …ìeya, …ìe lamndondira fii fiyaaku ma…ì…ìe on aduna."
  52,26,"∆Åe jaabora …ìe wiide : pellet, men laatino aduna, ko men hulunoo…ìe lepte Allah …óen, hakkunde yim…ìe amen …ìen."
  52,27,"Allah mo∆¥∆¥orii e amen, feewugol e lislaamu, O da…óandi men lepte norngal Yiite."
  52,28,"Men laatino e nguurndam amen aduna, me…óen rewaynoo Mo men toroo Mo da…óndugol men Yiite. Tawde pellet, ko Kanko woni mo∆¥∆¥o goongu…óo e ko O fodi jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen kon, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe. Hino jeyaa e ko O mo∆¥∆¥orii e amen O yurmii men : fewnugol men e gom…óinal, naada men Aljanna, wo…ó…óina men e Yiite."
  52,29,"An Nulaa…óo, anndintinir tun Alqur'aanaa, sabu ko neema gom…óinal e haqqil ko Allah ye…óu maa…óa kon, a wonaa ndureejo gollidoowo e jinna, a wonaa kadi feetu…óo."
  52,30,"Kaa …ìee fennoo…ìe wi'au wonnde : Muhammadu wanaa Nulaa…óo, ko yimoowo ! Mo men habbitanii tun biftagol maayde, men pooftoo e makko."
  52,31,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìe : awa habbitee maayde am ! Min kadi mi…óo habbitii nde lepte …óen yanata e mon, sabu ko fennu…óo lam kon."
  52,32,"Kaa ko haqqille ma…ì…ìe …óen yamiri …ìe wi'ugol : ko o ndureejo e feetu…óo? ∆Åe hawtita ko hawtitaa e ne…ó…óo. Si ko woni, …ìee yim…ìe yawtu…ìe tun keeri. ∆Åe ruttotaako e sari'a wanaa e haqqil."
  52,33,"Kaa …ìe wi'ay wonnde : Muhammadu tafu nde Alqur'aanaare, huunde wahayinaaka e makko? Oo'owoye... Si ko woni, …ìee ko townitanii…ìe gom…óingol nde, wa…ói si …ìe wiide o sincu nde."
  52,34,"Awa yo …ìe addii yewtere goo sugu mayre, hay si ko fefindaande, si wonii ko e goonga …ìe woni, wiide ko nde tafaande."
  52,35,"Kaa …ìe tagira …ìaawo tagoowo? Kaa ko kam…ìe woni tagu…ìe ko'e ma…ì…ìe? Pellet, huunde tagaaka …ìaawo tagu…óo nde, ko tagaa kadi tagataa. Ko ha…ói …ìe rewa tagu…óo …ìe on kisan?"
  52,36,"Kaa ko kam…ìe tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin? Ko woni goonga, …ìee yananaaka wonnde ko Allah tagi …ìe. Tawde si …ìe yanananoo …óum, …ìe wootin…óinanyno Mo, …ìe gom…óina Nulaa…óo Makko on."
  52,37,"Kaa …ìe jogiti ngaluuji arsike Joomi maa …óin, sakko …ìe salanoo …ói mo …ìe yi…óanaa? Maa Annabaaku ngun, sakko …ìe ye…óa ngun mo …ìe yi…óani, …ìe salanoo ngu mo …ìe yi…óanaa? Kaa ko kam…ìe woni hu…ìindii…ìe e piiji …óin, hara …ìe hi…ìe gerdira …ói no …ìe haajiri?"
  52,38,"Kaa …ìe jogiti ∆¥awirgal ka kammu, ngal …ìe he…óitorta wayahu Allah wi'oowo …ìe ko e goonga …ìe woni? Awa yo he…óitii…óo on e ma…ì…ìe addu on wahayu, wonndude e hujja …ìanngu…óo, goonginoowo ko nodditor…óon kon, wonnde ko e goonga won…óon."
  52,39,"Kaa hara ko …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe …ìe a√±an…óon ko'e mon …ìen, woodanta senii…óo On toowu…óo On, onon kan woodanii on …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe …ìen?"
  52,40,"Kaa a lamndi …ìe njo…ìdi, an Nulaa…óo, e ko yottinirtaa kon e ma…ì…ìe, immorde ka Joomi maa? Hara non …óum wontanay …ìe don≈ãgal ngal …ìe townataa?"
  52,41,"Kaa …ìe anndu fii wirnii…ói …óin, haa hi…ìe winndana yim…ìe …ìen, ko …ìe ∆¥ellitii e majji, …ìe humpita …ìe kala ko …ìen faalaa e mun?"
  52,42,"Kaa …ìee fennu…ìe faala fewjannde ma an e diina maa kan? Awa hoolo Allah. Tawde …ìen yeddu…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, ko kam…ìe woni fooletee…ìe pewje …ìen, wanaa an."
  52,43,"Kaa hi…ìe mari rewetee…óo goo e goonga, ko wanaa Allah? Allah senike O laa…ìii e kon ko …ìe dammbata e Makko, immorde e sirku ! Kala ko yawti kon, wanaa non woniri, ja…ìirtaake non kadi !"
  52,44,"Si …ìe yi'ii ta∆¥atine iwrunde ka kammu no yani, …ìe wi'a : ko duule fawondiri …óoo, wano woowiri non. ∆Åe ronka tasakaade maa …ìe gom…óina."
  52,45,"Nulaa…óo, accu…ìe e sattere feere ma…ì…ìe e yeddugol ma…ì…ìe, haa …ìe hawroya e √±alaande ma…ì…ìe nde …ìe leptoytee e mun. Woni √ëalnde Darngal."
  52,46,"√ëalnde nde pewje ma…ì…ìe …óen duncanoytaa …ìe hay huunde, …óuu…ói fan…ói, wanaa kadi …ìe faaboroytee…ìe da…óndeede lepte."
  52,47,"Ko pellet, hino woodani too√±ir…ìe ko'e mun …ìen sirku e geddi, lepte adii…óe lepte laakara …óen: …óen woni wareede e daheede, ka genaale kadi …ìe leptee. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude ko e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa …óum. Ko …óum wa…ói si …ìe √±ii…ìa e keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe."
  52,48,"An Nulaa…óo, mu√±√±o √±aawoore Joomi maa nden, e √±en∆¥al sari'a Makko on. Tawde pellet, hi…óa e ndenka Amen. Seninaa Joomi maa, tuma …ìa≈ãoto…óaa e …óoyngol maa."
  52,49,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinano…óaa Joomi maa, Juulanaa Mo, juulaa subaka on, tuma ka koode …óen mutirta …óon fee…óugol √±allal ngal."
